    "Following each activity, a quiz was administered via the LMS.",
    "In total, 175 students were enrolled in this course.",
    "All registered students provided informed consent but 158 students participated in all research activities, forming the research sample.",
    "Of these students, 102 (64.56%) were freshman from the Department of Statistics (corresponding to two sections), and 56 (35.44%) were sophomore from the Department of Computer Education and Instructional Technology (corresponding to one section).",
    "That is, this course was part of both departments' curricula at different academic years."
